license 'Apache2'
description 'The **nagios_config** module handles the configuration of nagios hosts
specifically it allows custom host variables to be set in the host definition, a usefull
nagios feature that is missing from the core nagios_host type'

## Add dependencies, if any:
dependency 'thias-nagios'
